claim.claim-text:
11. A poly interwoven spiral antenna comprises:
a plurality of interwoven spiral antenna units, wherein an interwoven spiral antenna unit includes a non-inverted spiral section having a spiral shape and an inverted spiral section having an inverted spiral shape;
a hub connection point;
a plurality of spoke connections, wherein a first end of a spoke connection of the plurality of spoke connections is coupled to a corresponding one of the plurality of interwoven spiral antenna units and a second end of the spoke connection of the plurality of spoke connections is coupled to the hub connection point, and wherein the second ends of the spoke connections are connected together at the hub connection point; and
a plurality of extension traces coupled to the plurality of interwoven spiral antenna units.
